# Per-platform cdylibs are never committed to this repo: the Go module proxy
# does not run git-LFS smudge filters, so LFS-tracked binaries reach `go get`
# consumers as pointer files, and plain git would bloat history. They are staged
# locally for `-tags embed_lib` builds (see lib/ in .gitignore) and attached to
# GitHub releases instead. See RELEASE.md.
